$IBIO I don't post on ST often anymore because the negativity and immaturity is astounding. But listen folks...if you are here bitching about the stock dropping and calling it a POS, that means you don't know how to trade. Period. I have made fantastic money off of this stock. So have the shorts. And no, shorts aren't evil, they're balance to the force. Reality is, no solid PR has dropped. This is a waiting game. Stocks don't just magically and steadily climb. ESPECIALLY bios. There are catalysts. Stop buying the top and holding like an idiot as it crashes. If you see it dropping (5% MAX), get out. Unless you are swinging long term with a very low average. Otherwise watch the L2s, buy in around support and wait. Come on. Get smart people. She has serious potential. But like anything, it's speculative. And we can only wait Bullish
